            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/mark_zandi_476907",
        "quote": "It has become fashionable to rail against government intervention in the economy, and the FHA is a favorite example by those trying to show the government's overreach. In reality, the FHA shows how government action during the Great Recession forestalled a much worse economic fate.",
